column2: Being able to assist our customers, especially during this challenging time, has always been of utmost importance for us at AIA Philam Life. With our hotlines and customer service centers temporarily suspended due to the enhanced community quarantine, we‚Äôve gathered your frequently asked questions regarding our services to still help you with your concerns. CLICK on the images below to learn more.

column2: So far, we have served over 100,000 meals to frontliners and communities in need through our Kindness Kitchens. This wouldn't have been possible without your do...nations. We are thankful for the support of our volunteers and partners, ABS-CBN, Coca-Cola, Angkas, Remington, Ecolab, TBWA, OMD, Leo Burnett, Seven A.D., PayMaya, Shopee, Isla, Liquigaz, Petron, Philam Foundation, Share Treats, M2Cash Corporation, and HAVI. column2: Train like a Spartan even at home! Join the daily virtual workouts of our Spartan Ambassadors -- live on Instagram! Check out the schedule below. Live a healthier, longer, better life with #PhilamVitality! Visit this link to find out more: http://bit.ly/PLVitality

We have partnered with Bayanihan Musikahan and Puhon: Ben&Ben to deliver PPES, test kits and transportation to those who need it the most. We are also supporting food security programs for those who have lost their capacity to earn. In doing so, we feel that we are able to fulfill our mission of helping Filipinos race against risk to live a healthier, longer, better life. We invite you to participate and give what you can to those who need it the most. Let us all do what we can to #FlattenTheCurve!
